org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles.impl
Class TextStyleImpl

java.lang.Object
  EObjectImpl
      org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles.impl.TextStyleImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
TextStyle
public class TextStyleImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements TextStyle

An implementation of the model object 'Text Style'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Underline
  • Underline Style
  • Strikeout
  • Font
  • Foreground
  • Background
  • Underline Color
  • Strikeout Color
